763
01:00:45,509 --> 01:00:50,185
Well, this all makes me so grateful.

764
01:00:51,515 --> 01:00:53,586
Seeing all you happy people...

765
01:00:53,750 --> 01:00:57,288
...who know how to love each other 
and take care of each other.

766
01:00:59,156 --> 01:01:03,195
I look at the amazing women I've met 
who I admire so much...

767
01:01:03,360 --> 01:01:08,469
...and the great men, 
taking care of their women...

768
01:01:08,632 --> 01:01:11,476
...and putting their children to bed.

769
01:01:12,969 --> 01:01:15,313
I just feel happy...

770
01:01:15,806 --> 01:01:19,481
...to see it and to be part of it

771
01:01:24,214 --> 01:01:27,320
I'm the luckiest girl in the world.

772
