-I fell asleep. 
-Yeah. Pity.

776
01:05:21,117 --> 01:05:25,361
Probably the only person in the world 
who ever fell asleep during meditation.

777
01:05:32,963 --> 01:05:36,570
-This leads to the meditation garden. 
-Is the guru here?

778
01:05:36,733 --> 01:05:40,112
-She's always here. 
-I know, but is she "here" here?

779
01:05:40,270 --> 01:05:42,375
She's at her ashram in New York

780
01:05:42,539 --> 01:05:44,917
But I came from New York 
to see her here.

781
01:05:45,075 --> 01:05:47,749
Sounds like one of her little tricks.

782
01:05:51,381 --> 01:05:53,759
The meditation cave.

783
01:05:53,950 --> 01:05:58,956
It’s open 2417
and it’s air-conditioned.

784
01:06:06,596 --> 01:06:08,473
Corella?

785
01:06:08,765 --> 01:06:12,474
-This is Liz Gilbert. 
-Hi. Nice to meet you.

786
01:06:16,106 --> 01:06:19,451
-Where did you get that button? 
-They sell them in the bookstore.

787
01:06:19,609 --> 01:06:23,182
That is exactly what I need. I need 
something like that. I don't listen.

788
01:06:23,346 --> 01:06:26,293
I never have. My mom used to 
call me Little Miss Chatty Cathy...

789
01:06:26,449 --> 01:06:28,360
...because I just ramble.
I am a rambler.

790
01:06:28,518 --> 01:06:31,431
I am rambling now. I'm sorry.

791
01:06:32,122 --> 01:06:34,124
Silence is a wonderful 
spiritual practice...

792
